aa(lp62
VIronically, at that time in my life,
p63
aVI was also doing cancer research,
p64
aVimmune-based therapies for melanoma, to be specific,
p65
aVand in that world I was actually taught to question everything,
p66
aVto challenge all assumptions
p67
aVand hold them to the highest possible scientific standards.
