aa(lp101
VWith that scare, I got busy changing my diet radically,
p102
aVadding and subtracting things most of you would find
p103
aValmost assuredly shocking.
p104
aVI did this and lost 40 pounds, weirdly while exercising less.
p105
aVI, as you can see, I guess I'm not overweight anymore.
