aVNow, imagine we thought bruises were the problem,
p169
aVand we evolved a giant medical establishment
p170
aVand a culture around treating bruises:
p171
aVmasking creams, painkillers, you name it,
p172
aVall the while ignoring the fact that people
p173
aVare still banging their shins into coffee tables.
